Hargrimm is leader of the skeletons of the Dead Nations, Hargrimm is a skeleton priest who speaks the words of the Silent King to his followers. With Stale Mary the zombie and Acaste the Ghoul-Queen as the two other corners, he makes the third of the triumvirate that holds the Dead Nations in uneasy balance. Tipping the balance one way or another might incite chaos. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
